          "markText": "成瘾的最大风险因素之一是成瘾物质容易获取。",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1779466004,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-23 00:06:44",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054893&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9749&rangeEnd=9770",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9e8321b0813ab7bf1g013230?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9749&rangeEnd=9770"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300054893_7_8061-8119",
          "range": "8061-8119",
          "rangeStart": 8061,
          "rangeEnd": 8119,
          "markText": "广义的“成瘾”是指，尽管对自己和/或他人有害，但仍然持续且强迫自己消费某种东西或做出某种行为（如赌博、游戏、性爱）。",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1779416376,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-22 10:19:36",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054893&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8061&rangeEnd=8119",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9e8321b0813ab7bf1g013230?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8061&rangeEnd=8119"
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "reviewId": "341822379_89ivlCFxH",
          "range": "13292-13305",
          "chapterName": "第1章 我们的自慰机",
          "content": "收到快递则天平转向。",
          "abstract": "消费行为本身也会让人上瘾。",
          "star": -1,
          "createTime": 1779466500,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-23 00:15:00",
          "isFinish": false,
          "chapterUid": 7
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "reviewId": "341822379_89hCrD5KB",
          "range": "6012-6035",
          "chapterName": "第1章 我们的自慰机",
          "content": "每种试图让自己快乐的事情都是如此，甚至高尚如读书写作也不例外。",
          "abstract": "从某种程度上来说，我们都在使用自己的自慰机器。",
          "star": -1,
          "createTime": 1779416202,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-22 10:16:42",
          "isFinish": false,
          "chapterUid": 7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "中文版序",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300054893_4_1011-1047",
          "range": "1011-1047",
          "rangeStart": 1011,
          "rangeEnd": 1047,
          "markText": "大脑中处理快乐和痛苦的区域是相同的，并且大脑会努力维持快乐和痛苦的平衡。",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1779325678,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-21 09:07:58",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1011&rangeEnd=1047",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9e8321b0813ab7bf1g013230?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1011&rangeEnd=1047"
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "reviewId": "341822379_89g2aXGlR",
          "range": "2134-2168",
          "chapterName": "中文版序",
          "content": "放弃快乐同时也意味着放弃痛苦，因为大脑会施加痛苦只为平衡你感受到的快乐。",
          "abstract": "放弃那些在短期内给他带来快乐的事情，从长远来看，可能会使他更加快乐。",
          "star": -1,
          "createTime": 1779326174,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-21 09:16:14",
          "isFinish": false,
          "chapterUid": 4
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "reviewId": "341822379_89g1VqKtF",
          "range": "1189-1207",
          "chapterName": "中文版序",
          "content": "作者解释的原因：多巴胺被释放以后，大脑会相应地减少或“下调”被刺激的多巴胺受体的数量，从而导致快乐-痛苦的天平向痛苦端倾斜，以恢复平衡。",
          "abstract": "常常会在快乐过后产生宿醉感或失落感。",
          "star": -1,
          "createTime": 1779325945,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-21 09:12:25",
          "isFinish": false,
          "chapterUid": 4
        }
      ]
    },
